Some staining tips:
-if the wood isn’t unfinished you will need to sand
-you can use a pre-stain conditioner or just stain with a microfiber rag (ours advised against using a paintbrush)
-apply all over product and be sure to wipe off any excess stain
-let the wood dry overnight 
-apply a sealer (optional)
